{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2028829, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 396196, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "怎么了", "timestamp": 1625828505, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2028839, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 396196, "reply_to": 2028829, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 湿热的北京七月，坚持学生必须穿长袖长裤作训服（有短袖作训服）；一上午医务室七人吸氧，有倒下口吐白沫的，有浑身颤抖哭着被抬上救护车的，但教官依然会因为一个同学没带武装带而罚全体太阳下站一上午军姿；三天洗一次澡，只有二十分钟洗澡时间，女生浴室门口有三个男老师维持秩序……这样的情况真实存在吗？军训该如何在保护学生和锻炼意志之间取得平衡？\n\n欢迎大家根据这次军训的实际体验进行回答，如有遗漏的不合理现象敬请补充，如有与事实不符的地方还请大家指正。\n\nhttps://www.zhihu.com/question/470351535/answer/1984008808", "timestamp": 1625828534, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2028853, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 396196, "reply_to": 2028839, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 😨😨", "timestamp": 1625828575, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2028861, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 396196, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "🤕🤕那本零字班同学感觉自己还好", "timestamp": 1625828629, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2028865, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 396196, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "天下苦军训基地久矣", "timestamp": 1625828656, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2028870, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 396196, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "北大军训也是长袖长裤", "timestamp": 1625828673, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2028875, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 396196, "reply_to": 2028861, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: +1 要真是像北外那样那个基地可能已经被清华同学给砸了", "timestamp": 1625828689, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2028880, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 396196, "reply_to": 2028870, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 对于其他惨剧来说不算什么了", "timestamp": 1625828715, "type": "text